Welcome to TLDGen
=================

To get a list of available commands-line arguments, execute "tldgen --help".

Example of use (all in the same line):

tldgen
	-sourcepath src/main/java
	-subpackages com.acme.tags
	-tldFile src/main/resources/META-INF/acme-core.tld
	-displayName "Acme Core Tag Library"
	-name acme-core
	-uri http://acme.org/acme-core.tld
	-htmlFolder build/docs/tlddoc
	
For any questions, go to the loom-users support group at 
http://groups.google.com/group/loom-users